						               													<description>Triage is a wonderful card game from the French publisher Grimaud who is more well known for his releases of traditional card games.&amp;#10;Aim of the game is to complete special trains and to score points for the best and longest of them.&amp;#10;This is done basically by drafting and discarding.&amp;#10;But what separates it from other games which are similar is a spinner with French train signals which will enhance or hinder your basic draw.&amp;#10;And you can steal an opponents train if you complete it using a set number of additional cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game components are of the finest sort: Super illustrated cards with locos and train cars from the steam area (featuring the famous Bugatti train...) before WW II and a patented card tray with golden applications.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
